Pable
=====
Create terminal tables with python.

Install
-------
not on pypi yet, so:
`[sudo] python setup.py install`

Usage
-----
```
from Pable import Table
# To generate a table, provide an array of arrays (which are interpreted as rows):
rows = []
rows.append(['One', '1'])
rows.append(['One', '1'])
rows.append(['One', '1'])
rows.render()
  # +-------+---+
  # | One   | 1 |
  # | Two   | 2 |
  # | Three | 3 |
  # +-------+---+
```
